snippet.title: Cardinal Quest 2 Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Cardinal Quest 2's coming to Steam!

Cardinal Quest 2 is a fast-paced turn-based hack 'n' slash, a super-sleek modern take on the classic roguelike formula, with plenty of stuff to keep you busy. Want to give it a spin?

http://cardinalquest2.com/
